#. type: Plain text
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/description.adoc:32
#: en/intro-to-gbif/modules/ROOT/pages/description.adoc:34
msgid "While efforts are made to provide materials in other languages, videos will be in English. Efforts are made to include subtitles when possible."
msgstr "雖然我們會盡力提供其他語言的資料，但影片將以英文呈現。我們會盡可能提供字幕。"

#. type: Title ==
#: en/intro-to-gbif/modules/ROOT/pages/data-access.adoc:1
#: en/intro-to-gbif/modules/ROOT/pages/description.adoc:14
#: en/intro-to-gbif/modules/ROOT/pages/solutions.adoc:106
#, no-wrap
msgid "Data access"
msgstr "資料存取"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/intro-to-gbif/modules/ROOT/pages/description.adoc:7
msgid "This course provides an introduction to GBIF, the data available in GBIF's portal, accessing that data and information about engaging with GBIF and its community of practice."
msgstr "本課程旨在介紹 GBIF、GBIF 入口網站中可用的資料、如何存取這些資料，以及如何與 GBIF 及其實務社群互動。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/intro-to-gbif/modules/ROOT/pages/description.adoc:11
msgid "Information about GBIF"
msgstr "關於 GBIF 的資訊"

#. type: Title ==
#: en/intro-to-gbif/modules/ROOT/pages/description.adoc:12
#: en/intro-to-gbif/modules/ROOT/pages/solutions.adoc:55
#, no-wrap
msgid "GBIF-mediated data"
msgstr "經由 GBIF 的資料"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/intro-to-gbif/modules/ROOT/pages/description.adoc:15
msgid "GBIF community of practice"
msgstr "GBIF 實務社群"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/intro-to-gbif/modules/ROOT/pages/description.adoc:17
msgid "This course is comprised of video and written instruction and paired with quizzes and practical exercises."
msgstr "本課程包含影片與文字教學，並搭配測驗與實作練習。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/intro-to-gbif/modules/ROOT/pages/description.adoc:24
msgid "This course is designed for anyone who is interested in using data from or publishing data to GBIF. It is particularly useful for those who have a desire to know more about GBIF and its place in the biodiversity community and want to engage further with GBIF."
msgstr "本課程專為對使用 GBIF 資料或向 GBIF 發布資料感興趣的使用者而設計。對於希望進一步了解 GBIF 及其在生物多樣性領域中的角色，並深入參與 GBIF 社群與相關合作活動的使用者而言，本課程尤其有幫助。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/intro-to-gbif/modules/ROOT/pages/description.adoc:32
msgid "There are no prerequisites for this course.  This course serves as a prerequisite for other GBIF courses."
msgstr "本課程無須具備任何先備知識，並可作為修習其他 GBIF 課程的基礎課程。"

